---
import Base from '../layouts/Base.astro';
import Header from '../components/Header.astro';
import Footer from '../components/Footer.astro';
---

<Base
  title="Disclaimer"
  description="Disclaimer for Njox blog — opinions, affiliate links, and accuracy of information."
>
  <Header />

  <main class="pt-28 pb-16 px-6">
    <div class="max-w-2xl mx-auto">

      <h1 class="font-serif text-3xl text-ink-900 dark:text-ink-50 mb-3">Disclaimer</h1>
      <p class="text-sm text-ink-400 dark:text-ink-600 mb-12">Last updated: March 2026</p>

      <div class="prose prose-ink dark:prose-invert prose-sm sm:prose-base max-w-none space-y-10">

        <section>
          <h2>Personal opinions</h2>
          <p>
            Everything on this blog represents my own personal views and opinions — not those of any
            employer, client, or company I am affiliated with. I write independently.
          </p>
        </section>

        <section>
          <h2>No professional advice</h2>
          <p>
            The content on this blog is for informational and educational purposes only. Nothing here
            constitutes legal, financial, medical, or professional advice of any kind. Always consult
            a qualified professional before making decisions based on anything you read here.
          </p>
        </section>

        <section>
          <h2>Accuracy</h2>
          <p>
            I do my best to ensure the information I publish is accurate and up to date. However,
            technology moves fast — especially in AI and software development. I make no guarantees
            that any post is complete, current, or error-free. If you spot a mistake, feel free to
            reach out and I'll correct it.
          </p>
        </section>

        <section>
          <h2>Affiliate links</h2>
          <p>
            Some posts on this blog contain affiliate links. If you click a link and make a purchase,
            I may earn a small commission at no extra cost to you. I only recommend products and
            tools I personally use or genuinely believe in. Posts containing affiliate links are
            clearly marked.
          </p>
        </section>

        <section>
          <h2>Sponsored content</h2>
          <p>
            Occasionally I publish sponsored posts — content that a company has paid to have featured
            on this blog. All sponsored posts are clearly labelled. Sponsorship does not influence my
            editorial stance; I retain full control over what I write and will not publish anything
            I disagree with.
          </p>
        </section>

        <section>
          <h2>External links</h2>
          <p>
            This blog links to third-party websites for reference and convenience. I have no control
            over the content or privacy practices of those sites and accept no responsibility for them.
          </p>
        </section>

        <section>
          <h2>Contact</h2>
          <p>
            If you have questions about this disclaimer, you can reach me at{' '}
            <a href="mailto:godblessnyagawa@gmail.com">godblessnyagawa@gmail.com</a>.
          </p>
        </section>

      </div>
    </div>
  </main>

  <Footer />
</Base>
